cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the problem of playlist recommendation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a multitask learning method that involves ranking and classification, which are relevant to sub-categories cs.CL and cs.SI. Finally, the paper uses real playlist datasets, which could be relevant to sub-category cs.CY (computers and society).
